    { q: 'Is there a registration fee required?', a: 'Yes, a nominal fee is required for certain premium events. Details will be provided upon initial registration.' },
    { q: 'Can I participate in multiple events?', a: 'Absolutely! You can select multiple events on the registration form as long as their timings do not clash.' },
